{"tid":2403720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為咗唔用「安心出行」而放棄所有娛樂，這並不是「抗爭」，而是斬腳趾避沙蟲～","createTime":"2021-02-11T08:56:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T11:57:31.000Z","uid":219007,"like":25,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"497d61ba9e3d84a15a6949ea1ebaa51011b9aa5a","tid":2403720,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:56:16.000Z","msg":"大家都係冇膽㗎啦，包括我同你都係一樣。<br />\n但係我同你地有一樣野唔同，就係我好誠實面對自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你香港人包括連登仔能夠一大班人，唔撚理佢，唔撚用APP，照衝入餐廳、戲院、遊樂場、主題樂園等等設施，繼續食飯跑步，有保安嚟到：「先生唔該...」 ，你堅持唔撚理佢甚至乎加多句：「行開啲啦屌你老母」繼續食飯繼續跑步繼續睇戲，咁呢個就真係叫做「抗爭」啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋將唔用個app而放棄睇戲食飯娛樂權利，並講到成為「抗爭」，其實只不過自我安慰。 呢啲並不是什麼「抗爭」，而是斬腳趾避沙蟲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋而家將斬腳趾避沙蟲嘅行為講成為「抗爭」<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，其實大家心底裏係因為唔憤氣，但又淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，於是乎將一啲好消極嘅行為包裝成為「抗爭」黎到讓自己好過啲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無架啦，條氣好唔順既？！ 放棄香港移民Lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個就係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c5b32ea8cb47a8f0669975991bd8e75d2c8118","tid":2403720,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b17585ce31444e6f5c2be591cb57cdc6941d8ca2","tid":2403720,"uid":114193,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:58:00.000Z","msg":"連下sir 唔係話唔好理香港變成點嘅咩？<br />\n做乜仲出咁多新聞post? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都想做港豬順民架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［改變心態］香港變成點唔重要，最緊要自己活得開心就足夠！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2368342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2368342</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後作為連下sir 信徒<br />\n幫手推廣下佢嘅概念<br />\n俾連登班黑暴知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聖誕節，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2329311/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2329311/page/1</a><br />\n肥佬黎俾人告國安法，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2323506/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2323506/page/1</a><br />\n中大畢業遊行，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2315353/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2315353/page/1</a><br />\n拜登贏咗，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2276817/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2276817/page/1</a><br />\n就黎國安法實行，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2184746/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2184746/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2073990/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2073990/page/1</a><br />\n612一周年，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2046361/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2046361/page/1</a><br />\n有武肺，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1850160/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1850160/page/1</a><br />\nPoly 打完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1768364/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1768364/page/1</a><br />\n要選區議會，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1681018/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1681018/page/1</a><br />\n機場壓力測試完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1548844/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1548844/page/1</a><br />\n8月大罷工完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1417635/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1417635/page/1</a><br />\n728元朗遊行完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1383029/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1383029/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"54f8633d6c19643408a0811951130503f7dd451f","tid":2403720,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:58:09.000Z","msg":"係咪盧斯達上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c70bb91e4794affe3cb1120b1dbf2daf35b85d","tid":2403720,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"54f8633d6c19643408a0811951130503f7dd451f","tid":2403720,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:58:09.000Z","msg":"係咪盧斯達上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:59:13.000Z","msg":"如果佢咁講我認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c0f7301553009e553bcc8f05babe3ada919775a","tid":2403720,"uid":374209,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10268649854ddfe3b72764c9e408fb125208af5c","tid":2403720,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T09:00:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392a4922ae4947fc3a1ca775f505e451aa78f6ca","tid":2403720,"uid":114193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T09:00:41.000Z","msg":"終於有每日一篇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba05f93c73d56a97764f1b144a6a43ecde9523f6","tid":2403720,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T09:02:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"662cf02761624e1ee3403929c75fc92fedd083e3","tid":2403720,"ui